+# ReelAI
+
+A modern iOS application for video sharing and management, built with SwiftUI and Firebase.
+
+## Features
+
+- Video upload and management
+- Real-time video feed
+- User profiles
+- Social interactions
+- Privacy controls
+- Efficient video processing and caching
